      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a class="btn" href="mailto:onoprecious247@gmail.com" target="_blank">Let's Talk Growth!</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/preciousono/" target="_blank" class="btn btn-outline ml-5">
